knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/03 3:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3051.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ac.gif" align=absmiddle>  Defense - Newbie Question</span><hr size=1> Something odd has happened to my defense - it's stuck at 197. I'm level 42, and I've been &quot;capped&quot; at 197 since 39, and no matter how much aggro I have and how many misses I generate, the skill doesn't seem to &quot;up&quot; at all. <br>
<br>
Was wondering if someone could comment on this oddity - I heard defense caps at 252, but do you have to be 50+ to get it above 200 (or, as may be the case, 197)?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=iskandaralazeem>Iskandar Alazeem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guardian of the Battlefield</BR>STEEL WARRIOR Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 1186<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/03 3:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3051.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ac.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Defense - Newbie Question</span><hr size=1> Think you're just having bad luck with your 197 defense skill atm, it should raise to 200. Once you hit 51 your defense skill will begin increasing again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=arothtb>Aroth TB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/03 4:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3051.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  .</span><hr size=1> Yep that's just par for the course I'm afraid (and not just for warriors) defence begins to get very sticky with it's raises as it nears 200.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=valoress>Valoress</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.defenders-of-the-realm.com/images/guildpics/Emeralde_Face.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/03 12:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3051.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: .</span><hr size=1> Try getting a KEI <br>
<br>
Whenever I want to practice a tradeskill, I grab a KEI.  It raises wis/int by 30.  Higher wis/int = higher chance for skill ups.  I don't see why it would not work for combat skills too. <br>
<br>
Just a thought  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=varaho1>Varaho1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 1432<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/03 1:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3051.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: .</span><hr size=1> Or better yet, get a dex buff for combat skills~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=baruchthebarbarianbastard>baruch the barbarian bastard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/22/03 5:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3051.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re:</span><hr size=1> I thought agility helped for raising defense, but I'll definitely try to sneak into a KEI in the Nexus next time I make it there ...  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=graalthedorf>Graal the Dorf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 216<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/23/03 3:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3051.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ale.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> Forget the KEI, get an AGI buff. Defense skill goes off of agility. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=14686">Graal MacBladefury</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
